    <h1>My Favorite Hobby: Playing Video Games</h1>
    <h2>Video Games</h2>
    <p> Video games are <u>electronic</u> games that requires a user interface, input device that generates visual feedback for the player or players, an output device that is either a two or three-dimensional display device.</p>
    <h3>my favorite game</h3>
    <p>I enjoy games like <b>Call of Duty</b>, <u>GTA</u>, and <i>BGMI</i>. <br>Each game offers a different challenge and lets me develop problem-solving skills in fun ways.</p>
    <h3>Benefits of playing video games</h3>
    <p>It will cover <u>cognitive</u>, social, and emotional advantages, such as improved <u>problem-solving skills</u>, enhanced hand-eye coordination, and opportunities for social interaction. The piece will also consider the educational potential of video games and their role in skill development.</p>
