    <h1>My Daily Routine</h1>
    <h2>Morning</h2>
    <p>I usually wake up around 6:30 AM and start my day with a glass of water and walk. <br>After that, I take a shower and have a healthy breakfast. <br>Then I check emails and plan my day before diving into study or work.</p>
    <h2>Afternoon</h2>
    <p>In the afternoon, I attend classes or complete assignments. <br>I usually take a break around 12:30 PM for lunch, followed by a short rest. <br>Later, I continue with my tasks or learning new things online.</p>
    <h2>Evening</h2>
    <p>In the evening I often play video games, go for a walk, or spend time with friends and family. <br>I have dinner around 8 PM. <br>I go to bed by 10:30 PM to stay fresh for the next day.</p>

